Haryana
Dec 13, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			Two minor girls were allegedly raped by their 20-year-old brother in the district, police said today.

In a complaint filed yesterday, the 14-year-old girl has alleged that she and her 12-year-old sister were repeatedly raped by their brother Ravindra since the last few months, they said.

The accused even allegedly threatened the victims with dire consequences if they reveal the incident to anyone, police said.

An FIR has been registered against Ravindra, who is absconding and efforts are on to nab him, they said.


